Product Description

The making of bamboo and cane products is perhaps the most universal of all the crafts practiced by a large number of artisans scattered throughout the North East States of India as Bamboo and Cane are grown in abundance here. Artisans create wonderful objects from very ordinary products without the usage of any mechanical device and it is completely eco-friendly. Some small irregularities in pattern weaving color design etc signifies these are handcrafted products and therefore are truely unique in nature. These are not machine crafted products. The acctual product might slightly vary from the picture.
